text: ཞང་སྟོན་བསོད་ནམས་གྲགས་པའི་གསུང་འབུམ། Works of Sonam Dragpa 雄滇·頌囊扎巴大師全集
zh-TW: 雄滇·頌囊扎巴大師全集
zh-CN: 雄滇·颂囊扎巴大师全集

nodes.en: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo'i 'grel ba snying po rab gsal zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
rgyud bla'i 'grel pa bka' 'khor lo tha ma'i gsal byed bzhugs/
chos rje zhang ston chen pos mdzad pa'i bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i cho ga dang sems bskyed bzhugs so/ /
sgra'i bstan bcos dkar po gling gi gzhung yol cags lo tsā bas mdzad pa dang / 'grel pa zhang ston gyis brag ram gyi gtsug lag khang du sbyar ba bzhugs/
legs sbyar sngags kyi klag thabs bzhugs so/ /
chos rje thams cad mkhyen pa'i bstod pa khyad 'phags nyid kyi lung rigs kyi bka' bab pa mkhas pa chen po zhang ston bsod nams grags kyis mdzad pa bzhugs so/ /
mkhan chen don grub dpal bzang po'i rnam thar bzhugs so/ /
phyag na rdo rje 'chi bdag 'joms pa 'chi bslu'i cho ga bzhugs so/ /
rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi drug cu pa'i gtor chog bzhugs so//
bshags chung rtsa brgyud ma bzhugs so/ /
rtsa ba'i ltung ba cha mthun dang bcas pa'i bskang bshags chen mo zhes bya ba bzhugs/
